          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "According to the Riverside County (California) District Attorney's Office, three California sheriff’s deputies and a towing company owner are facing felony charges for their alleged involvement in an illegal conspiracy and bribery scheme that included free (or heavily discounted) cars and other kickbacks. A report from ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
